  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for Experienced Candidate to join us for the below position:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Admin Assistant </strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Provide customer service and attend to phone / email enquiry as and when required</p>\n<p>. Processing of Delivery Order, Job Order, etc....</p>\n<p>. Prepare Quotation &amp; coordinate with customers</p>\n<p>. Inventory/ stock control</p>\n<p>. Assist in Marketing event such as cold calling &amp; Co-ordination etc</p>\n<p>. Provide general administrative to teams including filing, data entry and document management</p>\n<p>. Perform other ad-hoc administrative tasks as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Min Nitec/Diploma in Communication/ office management</p>\n<p>· At least 1-2 years relevant working experience</p>\n<p>· Must be a multi-tasker with good time management</p>\n<p>· <strong>Full of initiative, committed, meticulous and able to work independently</strong></p>\n<p><strong>without much Guidance, Good negotiation skills</strong></p>\n<p>· Computer literate in MS office, outlook</p>\n<p>· Those who can start immediately will be preferred</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates may send in their resume via whatsApp at HP no:96518935 or email to: hr@puricare.com.sg</p>",
